name: Pack of 12 Christmas Cards
description:
Twelve limited edition Christmas Cards, with two images per card of deer kissing, snowflakes and trees.  Each has a blank inlay and square envelope. Each pack has three red glitter, three silver glitter, three gold glitter and three green glitter.

	Only 100 cards printed up, when these are gawn they’re gawn.

	A free badge and sticker for each order too.
